Q.8:Predict output

odd=[2,4,6,8]
odd[0]=1         #1,4,6,8
print(odd)
odd[1:4]=[3,5,7] #[1,3,5,7]
print(odd)

O/P

[1, 4, 6, 8]
[1, 3, 5, 7]

Q.9: Predict output

odd=[1,3,5]
odd.append([7,9])
print(odd)
odd.extend([11,13])
print(odd)

O/p

[1, 3, 5, [7, 9]]
[1, 3, 5, [7, 9], 11, 13]


